column1: Description: The year and type of the last national household survey. Standard survey types: Demographic & Health Survey (DHS); Multiple Indicator Cluster Survey (MICS); Household Income & Expenditure Survey (HIES); National Survey (NS).
Source: IHSN Survey Catalog; USAID DHS Program.
